Gaborone &mdash; President Lt Gen. Dr Seretse Khama Ian Khama been seen off to Germany by Permanent Secretary to the President, Mr Carter Morupisi at the Sir Srertse Khama International Airport on March 6. President Khama will give a keynote address at the International Tourism Exhibition (ITB) in Berlin. Botswana has partnered with ITB Berlin to boost the country's international awareness as a tourism destination of choice. He is expected back home on Thursday, March 9.Source : BOPA